001E17  1               ; player_spr_data — 16x16 4bpp sprite, 128 bytes
001E17  1               ;
001E17  1               ;   Color 0 = transparent, Color 1 = white (default palette index 1)
001E17  1               ;   Design: classic upward-pointing triangular ship with engine notches
